@DATABASE CeeD.guide
@MASTER CeeD.doc

@NODE MAIN "Documentation for CeeD!"

Documentation for CeeD - an audio CD player for SCSI-2
compliant CD-ROM drives, with enhancements for SONY drives.

   @{" Author       " LINK AUTHOR}
   @{" Installation " LINK INSTALL}
